The paper addresses the problem of improving retrieval performance and search experience by automatically detecting the target types of entity-bearing queries. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a supervised learning approach with a rich variety of features, which indicates that it may also belong to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Databases (cs.DB), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
